content: I'm glad you provided me with some great info on documenting my collectibles. I think I'll start by taking photos of each item and creating a spreadsheet to catalog everything. I also want to look into getting some of my items appraised to get a more accurate value. By the way, I just remembered that I have 17 Star Wars action figures from the 80s, including a rare Boba Fett figure, which I think would be a great item to get appraised. Do you think that's a good idea?
